ActIndian Act
SubjectLand Exchange with respect to the Inuvik to Tuktoyaktuk Highway, Northwest Territories
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Indian Affairs and Northern Development to acquire, on behalf of Her Majesty, certain lands presently owned by the Inuvialuit Land Corporation that form part of the Inuvik to Tuktoyaktuk Highway in exchange for lands known as “Quarry lands”, the administration and control of which is to be relinquished, with the Governor in Council’s consent, by the Commissioner of the Northwest Territories and transfer the administration and control of the acquired lands to the Commissioner of the Northwest Territories.
